# Project Name -- Plot Overrides

Project-specific plot overrides for [project description]. Inherits from `styles/formats/static-plots.md` and `styles/labs/{lab}.md`.

## Scatter Plots

| Detail | Value | Rationale |
|--------|-------|-----------|
| Facet layout | `facet_wrap(~ Variable, ncol = 3)` | |
| PDF dimensions | 14 x 8 in | |
| Geom layers | `geom_smooth(lm)` + `geom_point()` | |

## Box/Violin Overrides

| Detail | Value | Rationale |
|--------|-------|-----------|
| Y-axis | `limits = c(0, NA)`, expand `c(0.05, 0.15)` | |
| Jitter | alpha 0.6, size 1.5 | |

## Output Dimensions

| Plot type | Width x Height (in) | Layout |
|-----------|---------------------|--------|
| Main scatter | 14 x 8 | 2x3 grid |
| Box/violin | 8 x 6 | -- |

All outputs saved as PDF. Primary output directory: `results/{project}/`
